Mark your calendars for Culture Fest 2025!
Join us for a night of film, food, and family fun as we celebrate Asian American, Pacific Islander, and Native Hawaiian Heritage Month!

When: Saturday, May 17 | 5 PM – 9 PM
Where: Ontario Museum of History & Art
FREE & open to all ages!

Come experience diverse stories, delicious bites, and vibrant cultural pride — all in one unforgettable evening!
